CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Presents Scholarship - MRs. Prather Hill, second from right, presents a check for $300 to pretty Yvonne Moore, winner of the Young Women's Achievement Club Scholarship Award this year. The presentation was made at the New Arena Club, Pittsburgh, as other members of the club look on.  Left to right: Mrs. William Smith, Mrs. James Downing, Miss Moore, Mrs. Samuel M. Walker, Mrs. Hill and Mrs. Oliver King. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Young Women's Achievement Club members, left to right: Mrs. William Smith, Mrs. James Downing, Yvonne Moore, receiving scholarship award, Mrs. Samuel M. Walker, Mrs. Prather Hill, and Mrs. Oliver King, standing in New Arena Club
